12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 5060.26, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 5060.26. A. A private, not-for-profit corporation may
15 be organized pursuant to the provisions of Title 18 of the Oklahoma
16 Statutes and the provisions of this act to develop the Industrial
17 Extension System in Oklahoma, with a special emphasis on minority
18 business enterprises. Such corporation, upon certification by
19 Oklahoma Futures, shall be known as and may exercise all of the
20 powers of OAME.
21 B. In addition to the provisions and requirements of Title 18
22 of the Oklahoma Statutes, the certificate of incorporation and the
23 bylaws of OAME must be certified by Oklahoma Futures and the
24 certificate of incorporation shall:
